'''鳳梨汁'''是由[[鳳梨|鳳梨]]{{le|果肉|Pulp (fruit)}}榨出的[[果汁|果汁]]。<ref name="morton">{{cite web|url=https://hort.purdue.edu/newcrop/morton/pineapple.html|title=Pineapple; In: Fruits of warm climates|date=1987|author=JF Morton|publisher=NewCROP, New Crop Resource Online Program, Center for New Crops and Plant Products, Department of Horticulture and Landscape Architecture, Purdue University|access-date=10 June 2019}}</ref>在制造过程中，黄梨汁通常是[[罐装|罐装]]的。<ref name=morton/>

它可直接饮用，也可以混合成[[冰沙|冰沙]]、[[鸡尾酒|鸡尾酒]]、烹饪风味和{{le|嫩肉剂|meat tenderizer}}。<ref name=morton/>黄梨汁也是[[凤梨可乐达|凤梨可乐达]]和''{{le|tepache}}''的主要成分。

