黄梨汁是由成熟的黄梨制成的。<ref name=morton/><ref name=juice>[http://ticomachine.com/faq/pineapple-juice-processing.html Pineapple juice processing complete sets of production lines] TICO, Retrieved June 10, 2019</ref>在榨汁前要清洗黄梨，使用刷子和喷雾清洁机去除污渍、瑕疵和农药残留。<ref name=production>[http://juicemakingmachine.com/complete-line/pineapple-juice.html Pineapple juice processing line] TICO, Retrieved June 10, 2019</ref>清洗干净后，将黄梨放入黄梨去皮榨汁机中，获得果肉，再放入螺旋榨汁机中。<ref name=production/>然后，使用果汁精细过滤器去除黄梨汁中的所有固体、纤维和胶体颗粒。<ref name=morton/><ref name=production/> 

黄梨汁粉末是由黄梨汁{{le|喷雾干燥|spray drying}}于{{le|木薯根淀粉|Tapioca}}的[[麦芽糊精|麦芽糊精]]上并使其干燥而成的。<ref name=powder>[https://www.spicesinc.com/p-8970-pineapple-juice-power.aspx Pineapple Juice Powder] Spices, Inc. Retrieved June 12, 2019</ref>

==烹饪==
黄梨汁可用于[[派|派]]、[[蛋糕|蛋糕]]、[[玛芬|玛芬]]、[[司康饼|司康饼]]、[[酸辣酱|酸辣酱]]、[[果酱|果酱]]、[[辣豆酱|辣豆酱]]、[[糖果|糖果]]、[[酱汁|酱汁]]和[[浓汤|浓汤]]。它也用于[[腌泡|腌泡]][[鸡|鸡]]和[[鱼|鱼]]。<ref name=powder/>

==市场==
2016年，[[欧盟|欧盟]]消费了50%的黄梨汁。<ref name="eu">{{cite web |title=Exporting pineapple juice to Europe |url=https://www.cbi.eu/market-information/processed-fruit-vegetables/pineapple-juice |publisher=Centre for the Promotion of Imports, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, Government of the Netherlands |access-date=12 June 2019 |date=13 December 2017}}</ref>[[荷兰|荷兰]]是2016年[[欧洲|欧洲]]最大的菠萝汁进口商。<ref name=eu/>[[泰国|泰国]]和[[哥斯达黎加|哥斯达黎加]]则是2016年欧盟市场的主要供应国。<ref name=eu/>2017年，黄梨汁消费量最多的国家是[[泰国|泰国]]、[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]]和[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]，合计消费量占世界总量的47%。 <ref name="agri">{{cite web|url=https://www.agriorbit.com/population-growth-drives-gradual-expansion-of-pineapple-juice-market/|title=Population growth drives gradual expansion of pineapple juice market|publisher=AgriOrbit|access-date=22 May 2019|date=21 January 2019}}</ref>与它们的人口相比，[[中国|中国]]和[[印度|印度]]的黄梨汁消费量较低。<ref name=agri/>

==饮料==
Tepache是由黄梨的皮和核、[[甘蔗|甘蔗]]和[[肉桂|肉桂]]制成的。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/food/2018/dec/01/how-to-turn-pineapple-skin-into-a-refreshing-drink|author=Tom Hunt|title=How to turn pineapple skin into a refreshing drink|work=The Guardian|access-date=11 June 2019}}</ref>凤梨可乐达是一种[[鸡尾酒|鸡尾酒]]，由[[兰姆酒|兰姆酒]]、[[椰浆|椰浆]]和黄梨汁组成。<ref>[https://piteliaxitelia.wordpress.com/2013/06/27/the-strained-pineapple-history-of-pina-colada/ The "Strained Pineapple"....History of Pina Colada] Piteliaxitelia Retrieved June 11, 2019</ref>

